Energy Assets Group Plc Key Developments

Energy Assets Group Plc's Ordinary Shares Cancel From Admission To Trading On The LSE
Jul 6 16
Energy Assets Group Plc announced that its ordinary shares of 1 pence each fully paid have been cancelled from admission to trading on the LSE with effect from July 6, 2016 8.00 AM.


