Menu

Gas emergency?





















Metering, energy data and network services for Britain's energy and utilities market


Scroll to content


     










Design, install, maintain and monitor advanced metering systems - from new installations and Automated Meter Reading (AMR) to gas networks and complex downstream projects.
GAS









Advanced metering and new connections for electricity customers incorporating meter operator (MOP), data collection and aggregation (DC/DA) services.
ELECTRICITY









Connections, meters and AMR services for both fiscal and submetering applications.  Ask us about our free water audit services.
WATER









Efficiently managing energy usage by taking control of local loads.
CONTROL









Our Mission
To be the leading provider of multi-utility Industrial & Commercial (I&C) metering and network services, delivering efficiency, innovation and value.




Why Work with us?










End to End
It is our ability to deliver true ‘end-to-end’ support for Britain’s businesses and public service providers that sets us apart. We design and manage energy utility networks (upstream and downstream of the meter), install advanced metering and collect and deliver energy consumption data through automated meter reading systems.









Operational Efficiency
Energy Assets is one of Britain’s leading and fastest growing independent metering businesses. We help private and public sectors to improve their energy efficiency through groundbreaking technologies, real-time data and innovative customer centric processes.









Compliance
Everything we do is fully compliant with the relevant legislative and industry standards – supported by a robust internal and external audit regime.









Industry Expertise
We have assembled a team of industry experts and we continue to invest in the development of our people to meet and exceed the needs of our customers.





 


Multi-Utility
Our multi-utility service delivery across gas, electricity and water provides customers with a bundled proposition from a trusted service provider.
From our accredited design team through to fiscal or submetering and compliance ready consumption data delivered to your desk, Energy Assets' service will reduce upfront costs, enabling work to be carried out efficiently by one party.
VIEW MULTI-UTILITY SOLUTIONS
 







We’re leaders in our sector and have the evidence to prove it
We work closely with our customers to provide multi-utility network and metering services.
Browse Our Case Studies
 








Energy Assets Utilities – Focused on Energising Britain’s Utility Networks
There’s a new name in multi-utility network design, engineering and construction across Britain.
 
Read about EA Utilities
 
