Energy Assets Group PLC Company Profile

 
			

Get an in-depth profile of Energy Assets Group PLC, including a general overview of the company's business and key management, as well as employee data and location and contact information.









 


IndustryBusiness Services
SectorServices
Employees181
Equity TypeORD


Energy Assets Group plc is an independent provider of industrial and commercial (I&C) gas metering services in the United Kingdom. The Company also provides utility infrastructure services, and electricity metering and data services. The Company's divisions include Meter Asset Management division, Siteworks division and Data Services division. The Company offers a range of metering services from the provision and management of new and replacement meters through its Meter Asset Management division to utility suppliers and end user consumers of energy for the procurement and project management of related gas infrastructure works. Through its Siteworks division, the Company provides a consultancy, system design and project management service for gas infrastructure works and meter point infrastructure. The Company collects and provides energy consumption data through its Data Services division.


Contact Information


Address
6 Almondvale Business ParkAlmondvale WayLivingston, EH54 6GAUnited Kingdom



Phone
+44-1506-405405



Fax
+44-1506-416629



Web
www.energyassets.co.uk




